text: Farai Mudariki (born 13 February 1995) is a Zimbabwe rugby union player. His usual position is as a Prop, and he currently plays for Worcester Warriors. ==References== ==External links== *itsrugby.co.uk Profile Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean rugby union players Category:Zimbabwe international rugby union players Category:Rugby union props
